pan\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Mysore Pak - \u003c\/strong\u003eCashew, milk, Ghee, Sugar\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSuryakala -\u003c\/strong\u003e Wheat, Almond, Cashew, milk, Ghee, Sugar\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cb\u003eStorage Instructions\u003c\/b\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore in a cool and dry place\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":44745148006680,"sku":null,"price":315.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"500 Gms","offer_id":44745147973912,"sku":"501","price":630.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0722\/9692\/3416\/files\/Sohanpapdi_b58b2368-930e-46c2-8edf-43b17e0908d1.png?v=1771686408"},{"product_id":"khova-gujia","title":"Khova Gujiya","description":"\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eA Timeless Delight\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIndulge in the traditional flavor of Dadu’s Khoya Gujiya, a beloved deep-fried sweet that has been a favorite across the Indian subcontinent for centuries. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade with suji, each gujiya is stuffed with a sweet mixture of khoya (milk solids), freshly grated coconut, dried fruits, and a hint of suji for a grainy texture. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFried to a perfect crisp in desi ghee, this half-moon shaped delicacy offers a delightful combination of textures and flavours that will leave you craving more.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAt Dadu's, we ensure that you can shop our premium sweets online with ease.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOur Khoya Gujiya is delivered to your 